3. cs.LG (Machine Learning): The paper proposes an LSTM-based model for trajectory prediction, which is a machine learning technique. 
4. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper deals with developing autonomous systems that can anticipate human motion, which is a key application of artificial intelligence. 
5. cs.SD (Software Engineering): Although not the primary focus, the paper may involve software engineering aspects related to implementing the proposed model in real-world systems.
